&lt;img alt=&quot;双色调紫色背景上的 SAG-AFTRA 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HI-nveCZrFEYNIzOEKVW9r5mbd8=/0x0:3001x2001/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72855271/STK159_SAG_AFTRA_03.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插画：William Joel / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;irGFI8&quot;>;美国演员工会-美国电视和广播艺术家联合会 (SAG-AFTRA) &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/8/23945647/hollywood-actors-sag-aftra-strike-contract-deal&quot;>;与好莱坞制片厂高管达成暂定协议&lt;/a>;，有效结束了&lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/17/23798246/strike-hollywoods-writers-actors-wga-sag-aftra&quot;>;为期 118 天的演员罢工&lt;/a>;。昨天，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sagaftra.org/sag-aftra-national-board-approves-tentative-agreement-recommends-ratification-2023-tvtheatrical&quot;>;SAG-AFTRA 宣布&lt;/a>;国家委员会以 86% 比 14% 的投票结果批准了该协议，并建议工会成员投票批准。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ChKrXG&quot;>;该协议在技术上仍处于等待状态，直到 12 月 5 日统计工会成员的投票结果为止。 ，尽管该协会表示其一些功能将在批准过程中生效，例如某些加薪。 SAG-AFTRA 在其公告中提供了交易摘要：&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;ukrpZS&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component= &quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;好莱坞演员仍在罢工&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7 /17/23798246/strike-hollywoods-writers-actors-wga-sag-aftra&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;JrsQ1T&quot;>; &lt;strong>;流媒体收入：流媒体节目的收入&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/14/23795311/hollywood-strike-wga-sag-aftra-streaming&quot;>;巨大公会战斗的一部分。公会称其“实现了......&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23956660/sag-aftra-actors-strike -deal-approved-streaming-revenue-ai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23956660/sag-aftra-actors-strike-deal-approved-streaming-revenue-ai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23956660/sag-aftra-actors-strike-deal-approved-streaming-revenue-ai</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-11T10:15:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-11T10:15:00-05:00</updated><title>咄咄逼人的结帐屏幕正在助长“通货膨胀”</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Panera 提示屏幕&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yjylaqdA8hAlNrgqvVtHIRhn1ac=/0x0:4032x2688/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/72854827/IMG_2659.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Panera 的小费提示稍好一些，因为您可以选择美元金额，并且有披露称您的小费“可能”会分发给符合条件的员工.&lt;/em>; |摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UGQBnU&quot;>;给小费是美国一项古老的争论。您支付多少钱以及何时支付？这是一种选择还是一种义务？总的来说，多年来，科技至少让这一切变得更加容易。智能手机让朋友们可以轻而易举地拿出计算器来算出小费并分摊账单。现在，从实体商店到送货应用程序，各地的结账屏幕都添加了旨在让您更轻松地支付小费的按钮。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;LS6hQN&quot;>;这很方便，但事实并非如此。根据皮尤研究中心的一份新&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pewresearch.org/2023/11/09/tipping-culture-in-america-public-sees-a-changed-landscape/&quot;>;报告&lt; /a>;，美国的小费文化近年来发生了转变。百分之七十二的美国人表示，与五年前相比，更多的地方需要给小费。并非所有这些都与技术相关，但很难否认&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/news/tipping-culture-etiquette-evolving-with-gratuity-screens-everywhere/#:~ :text=技术%20has%20played%20a%20large%20role%20in%20change%20the%20rules%20around%20tipping.%20Touch%20screens%20with%20tip%20prompts%20are%20increasing%20replacing%20old%2Dfashioned%20tip% 20jars%2C%20which%20were%20easier%20to%20slip%20past%20and%20ignore.%20and%20on%20a%20screen%2C%20you%20have%20to%20actively%20reject%20the%20request.%C2%A0&quot; >;结帐屏幕在小费膨胀中的作用&lt;/a>;。甚至...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955381/checkout-screens-tipping-pos-kiosk&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955381/checkout-screens-tipping-pos-kiosk" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955381/checkout-screens-tipping-pos-kiosk</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-11T09:00:09-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-11T09:00:09-05:00</updated><title>洛基第二季大结局深入挖掘漫威所有疯狂的意义</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个男人站在未来房间的中央，面前是一排窗户。这个男人周围的一切似乎都在分解成线。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/53QI5s-BkcfgByYBSxoHVFyLL18=/589x0:3211x1748/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72854608/EET3200_205_comp_FRA_v0380 .2364_R__1_.0。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;漫威&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;洛基的第二季以巨大的、存在主义的爆炸声结束，为恶作剧之神在漫威多元宇宙的中心赋予了光荣但令人困惑的新目标。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23955559/loki-season-2-finale-review-disney-plus-marvel-mcu-kang&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23955559/loki-season-2-finale-review-disney-plus-marvel-mcu-kang" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23955559/loki-season-2-finale-review-disney-plus-marvel-mcu-kang</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-11T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-11T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>苹果的中端“Pro”M3芯片看起来并不是一个巨大的升级</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple M3 芯片图解&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Z4XBdDqqyX25S0SseCSKLRE8uUI=/188x0:2213x1350/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/ chorus_image/image/72854565/Apple_M3_chip_series_screen.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;M3 Pro 并不像您期望的那样中频。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Yb2Nr1&quot;>;Apple 的新款 M3 Pro 芯片看起来就像一只奇怪的鸭子 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23944344/ apple-macbook-pro-14-2023-review-m3-specs-battery-ports&quot;>;大幅改进&lt;/a>; MacBook Pro 笔记本电脑。对于大多数需要一台功能强大的计算机来胜过沉闷的办公任务并需要多个外部显示器的人来说，M3 Pro 可以满足他们的需求，并且拥有强大的电池启动能力。但是，可能已经拥有配备 M2 Pro 芯片甚至 M1 Pro 的 Mac 的逐年计算机升级者可能不会看到很多（如果有的话）性能改进，除非他们 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /23949207/apple-macbook-pro-16-m3-max-review-price-specs&quot;>;为 M3 Max 投入更多资金&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;NQvbtg&quot;>;当你投入时如果将 12 核 M2 Pro 和 M3 Pro 进行正面对比，您可能会认为后者的性能要好得多。事实上，M3 Pro 并没有放弃旧芯片。这是因为一个有趣的设计选择：苹果将其平均分配为六个...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955727/apple -m3-pro-macbook-chip-mid-small-upgrade&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955727/apple-m3-pro-macbook-chip-mid-small-upgrade" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/11/23955727/apple-m3-pro-macbook-chip-mid-small-upgrade</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-11T08:27:32-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-11T08:27:32-05:00</updated><title>索尼舒适的 LinkBuds S 耳机限时最低价</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;白色索尼 LinkBuds S 无线耳机及其充电盒位于木桌边缘。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AObzxZ2acPhNy5hsk0SRf_f4eTM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72854493/DSCF7983.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;轻盈透气的 LinkBuds S 黑色版本仅需 108.80 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;6fGO7K&quot;>;您可能会认为黑色星期五前的两周不是获得科技产品最佳价格的好时机，但由于大量交易都在下降提早去购物也没什么坏处。例如，&lt;strong>;Sony LinkBuds S&lt;/strong>;无线耳机的价格再次降至最低价。您只需 &lt;a href=&quot;https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=nOD%2FrLJHOac&amp;amp;mid=44583&amp;amp;u1=verge&amp;amp;murl=https%3A 即可购买索尼超轻舒适的黑色耳机%2F%2Fwww.newegg.com%2Fsony-linkbuds-s-wireless-black%2Fp%2F0TH-000U-00HN5&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Newegg 108.80 美元（折扣 90 美元）&lt;/a >;。或者，如果您喜欢更明亮的颜色选项，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09YL296PM?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;spoken noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/ a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fp%2Fsony-linkbuds-s-true- wireless-bluetooth-noise-canceling-earbuds-white%2F-%2FA-86314265&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; 